casebody.data:
Edward MOZIE, Petitioner,
v.
The STATE of Florida, Respondent. No. 3D15-0434 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. Opinion filed March 6, 2019 Edward Mozie, in proper person. Ashley Moody, Attorney General, for respondent, the State of Florida. Before SALTER, LINDSEY, and MILLER, JJ. MILLER, J.

Upon review of the petition for writ of habeas corpus, it is ordered that said petition is dismissed. See Baker v. State , 878 So.2d 1236 (Fla. 2004).
